### ===========================================
### CUSTOMER ENDPOINTS
### ===========================================

### Get all customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/customers
Accept: application/json

###

### Get customer by ID (replace with actual UUID after creating one)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/customers/{{customerId}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "age": 28,
  "weight": 75,
  "height": 180,
  "gender": "Male",
  "exerciseDays": "FOUR_DAYS"
}

###

